quran[2]{c,v,t}:
  2,60,WE ‘IDH ESTESKA MUSA LIKAWMIHI FEKULNA EDRIB BI’ASAKEL-HEXHERE FANFEXHERET MINHU ETHNETA ‘ASHRETE ‘AJNÆN KAD ‘ALIME KULLU ‘UNASIN MESHREBEHUM KULU WE ESHREBU MIN RIZKI ELLAHI WE LA TA’THEW FIL-’ERDI MUFSIDINE
  2,61,WE ‘IDHI KULTUM JA MUSA LEN NESBIRE ‘ALA TA’AMIN WAHIDIN FAD’U LENA REBBEKE JUHRIXH LENA MIMMA TUNBITUL-’ERDU MIN BEKLIHA WE KITHTHA’IHA WE FUMIHA WE ‘ADESIHA WE BESELIHA KALE ‘ETESTEBDILUNEL-LEDHI HUWE ‘EDNA BIEL-LEDHI HUWE HAJRUN EHBITU MISRÆN FE’INNE L